  {
    "type": "main-inset-br",
    "page": "phone_40",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "PHONE BED",
        "zh": "手机托架"
      },
      "small": "phone_40"
    },
    "main": {
      "src": "phone_40_bed_frame_assembled_cam0.svg",
      "style": "transform: translateX(-35mm);"
    },
    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Install the phone bed",
          "zh": "安装手机托架"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Stand the frame on end first — it's far easier to work vertically. Then slide each beam's T-nuts into the slots on the frame's underside.",
          "zh": "先把框架竖起来——立着干活要省事得多。再把每根横梁上的 T 型螺母滑进框架底面的型材槽里。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "right:30mm; top:22mm; width:90mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Position the phone",
          "zh": "放手机"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Place a phone on the bed, pushed into the top-left corner. Jog the X carriage across its full travel and check the stylus tip can reach every part of the screen.",
          "zh": "把手机放到托架上，左上角靠齐内角。让 X 滑座走完整个行程，确认触控笔尖能够到屏幕的每个位置。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "right:30mm; top:50mm; width:90mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Dial in the tap",
          "zh": "调好点击力度"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "The tip must tap firmly enough to register, but no harder. Too hard can crack the screen; too far or too light and the tap misses. Adjust the solenoid mount height until taps land reliably.",
          "zh": "笔尖点下去的力度，要刚好让屏幕能识别，再大就过了。太用力会把屏幕压裂；离太远或太轻又会点不到。调整电磁铁安装高度，直到每次都能稳稳点中。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "right:30mm; top:85mm; width:90mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Keep the screen flat",
          "zh": "让屏幕保持水平"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "The rear camera bump lifts one corner, so the phone won't lie flat. Slip a thin shim or a few sheets of paper under the low edge until the screen is level and facing straight up. Make sure the phone can't rock or shift when the stylus taps — any tilt or wobble can make it miss.",
          "zh": "后置摄像头那块凸起会把一个角顶起来，手机就放不平。在偏低的那一边垫一片薄垫片或几张纸，直到屏幕水平、正对上方。还要确保点击时手机不会晃、不会移位——只要有一点歪或松，就可能点不准。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "right:30mm; top:124mm; width:90mm; display:flex; gap:4mm; align-items:flex-start;",
        "icon": "info"
      }
    ]
  }
]